Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.player.synthesizer

Class Synthesizer

java.lang.Object
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.player.synthesizer.Synthesizer
public class Synthesizer extends Object
Represents a synthesizer, or a note block builder that allows to create songs using a string.
